Metadata: Directory Update: New Research, Outreach and Partnership Projects for 2003-2004
University of Washington Sea Grant Program
program reports (annual, progress, planning reports, etc)

The projects listed in this document have been initiated since February 2001, when the 2001-2004 Research, Outreach & Partnerships directory was compiled and distributed. The projects have been grouped by Critical Program Area: Living Marine Resources, Ecosystem Health, New Technologies, Economic and Community Development and Education, and Training and Public Information.
